								
								***** NetMouse *****
                                  (Network Mouse)
								  
Enables to use mouse and keyboard from target computer on remote computer as 
its was like additional screen.

Program works in client/server way for sending/receiving events for mouse or 
keyboard through network.

Meanwhile it works only on WinNT system.
MinGW is used as build tool.

								***** HOWTO USE *****
For receiving events on remote machine simply run netmouse.exe.
For connect to remote computers screen you should run netmouse.exe with -s option
, where -s means server address
